          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1607951226829-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash the<strong> gem lettuce</strong>, then remove 4<span class=\"text-danger\"> [8]</span> leaves and set them aside and pat them dry with kitchen paper, then cut the <strong>remaining lettuce</strong> into wedges</p><p>Once the chips have had an initial 20 min, create some space on the tray and put the <strong>meat-free burger patties</strong> in the oven for an initial 10 min or until almost cooked through</p><p>Tip: If you're cooking for 4, you may need to cook your patties on a separate tray!</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1607951233424-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
