      "instruction": "<p>Once the meat-free bacon is crispy, chop <strong>half </strong>of it finely (save the full rashers for the burger!)</p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped meat-free bacon </strong>with the<strong> chopped rosemary leaves </strong>– this is your <strong>rosemary & meat-free bacon crumb</strong></p>",
