    {
      "instruction": "<p>To assemble, fill the <strong>toasted brioche halves </strong>with the<strong> chilli mayo</strong>, <strong>cheezy patties</strong>, <strong>reserved</strong> <strong>crispy meat-free bacon rashers</strong>, <strong>tomato slices </strong>and <strong>outer lettuce leaves </strong>– these are your<strong> plant-based bacon cheezeburgers</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> lettuce wedges</strong> and <strong>fries</strong> to the side, then spoon the <strong>caramelised onions</strong> and <strong>rosemary & meat-free bacon crumb </strong>over the fries – these are your<strong> fancy fries</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
